column5: I have been a lurker for a while and really enjoy the converstions on the old board.  I have joined to new board and really like the look of it.  I look forward to getting to know a lot a members and meet you in person.  I live in Oakville and love to fish Bass and Walleye.  Kudo's to you all for a great board.  needtofish
welcome needtofish   Nice to see you finally posting.
Welcome to the board,  'needtofish' .........and thanks for the kind comments about it!
Welcome needtofish!!!!  This has become my home away from home....geez...I need to get out more....

Welcome needtofish  I am in Burlington, shoot me a PM if you want to get out fishing sometime.  Also, keep an eye out for the OFC Christmas Swill that should be taking place near the end of December.  If you can make it out to that you should be able to put some faces to names from some of the fish-a-holics from here.  Tony
Welcome to the show that never ends, enjoy your stay and don't mess with the bull, he gets real mean
Welcome aboard and we all needtofish ... don't we ?
Glad you like our new digs.. Welcome aboard !!
Welcome needtofish! You will have a great time here!
welcome aboard. hope to see many pics. cheer and great fishing
Welcome aboard and enjoy the ride.  Regards, Sam
